Class TriggerInstanceEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wegas.core.persistence.AbstractEntity
      • com.wegas.core.persistence.variable.VariableInstanceEntity
        • com.wegas.core.persistence.variable.statemachine.StateMachineInstanceEntity
          • com.wegas.core.persistence.variable.statemachine.TriggerInstanceEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    @Entity
public class TriggerInstanceEntity
extends StateMachineInstanceEntity
    Trigger: S1->(T1)->S2, S2 final (oneShot)
    S1->(T1)->S2->(!T1)->S1 (opposedTrigger)
    else S1->(T1)->S1 (loop).
    OneShot and OpposedTrigger are exclusive. OneShot wins.
    Author:
    Cyril Junod
